  "body": "Consider, \n\n```\nhelm create mariadb\ncd mariadb\ngit init\n# hack and commit\ncd ../\nhelm package mariadb\n```\n\nThe `.git` metadata ends up being packaged in the chart release. Maybe an optional `.helmignore` file can be defined in the chart directory to indicate files that should not be package in releases similar to `.gitignore` or `.dockerignore`.\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
